{"tid":207681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州男子迷信偏方 將黃鱔塞入肛門通腸","createTime":"2017-04-19T04:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T05:54:40.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a05086fab2806818365194e874c03acc6ad2c804","tid":207681,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:38:50.000Z","msg":"中國大陸廣東省廣州49歲劉姓男子日前因腹痛就醫。經手術，醫生從他身體取出一條<br />\n長50公分、頭部直徑3至5公分的黃鱔。男子表示，聽說黃鱔可以通腸，才把牠塞進肛門。<br />\n <br />\n    廣州日報今天報導，劉姓男子上星期一路小跑衝進廣州白雲區東仁醫院，說自己腹痛<br />\n難忍，醫生馬上對他動手術。劉先生當時腹部鼓脹，手術發現滿肚子都是糞便、糞水、食<br />\n物殘渣。<br />\n <br />\n    更讓醫生們驚訝的是，劉姓男子肚子裡出現一條長50公分的黃鱔，足足有250公克，<br />\n頭部直徑達3至5公分，而且整條黃鱔都在腹腔裡。幸虧即時動手術，這名廣州「黃鱔哥」<br />\n才得以死裡逃生。<br />\n <br />\n    醫生詢問原因，劉姓男子一開始說黃鱔是自己跑進肛門的；進一步追問後，劉姓男子<br />\n才鬆口說，因為自己腸阻塞，民間偏方說透過鱔魚的黏滑度，在腸道內蠕動一下就可以治<br />\n療，才會動手嘗試。<br />\n <br />\n    有網民懷疑劉姓男子將黃鱔塞入肛門的動機。有人表示，「通腸藥每瓶才（人民幣）<br />\n1塊錢（新台幣約4.5元），黃鱔50元1斤」；還有網民調侃，這則新聞「看得我括約肌一<br />\n緊」，「想知道黃鱔的心理陰影面積」。"},{"pid":"605b36cb40fee9be335279a17309576dd059fe7d","tid":207681,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6580fad7a9a8e53d9d66699f79ddd4c674985b","tid":207681,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:42:33.000Z","msg":"識玩一定玩油追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1dd72e850594ee556c80d04b82af26d5c4db45","tid":207681,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"古法自殺"},{"pid":"d611261a579b72ac7d4200ec01d1b0b050adaa6f","tid":207681,"uid":93640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"玩到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c9dc1bbf0849185571c1d13098b83f5f915f66","tid":207681,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"自慰咪認囉，好柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b2825e916fcbe00af1208f76dedebc4ea2461b","tid":207681,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識玩一定玩油追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8Tmnv3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8Tmnv3.jpg&h=fc01a9d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb46a03be35ba5a08598b9b8fe05c5a99154ca79","tid":207681,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe7d4e0ea43e998ea1810a937b38416634c27da","tid":207681,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"黃鱔都得，咁condom都得喇"},{"pid":"edd03a277d0f07adf01a27240ff7c07579c87451","tid":207681,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"用電鰻先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e8a961d801597bef0844fb62062374eb21183d","tid":207681,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃鱔都得，咁condom都得喇</blockquote><br />\nCondom都得，咁689都得啦"},{"pid":"4b79123f213aaefd7327818ec81b0f234ffe511f","tid":207681,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:34:16.000Z","msg":"講還講.jpg"},{"pid":"e7db8f687dfca6b580624f696694e3c49e37628f","tid":207681,"uid":34308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"古法自殺"},{"pid":"afb225c6c35ebedbbb0fdc14b7dc431a0913c45b","tid":207681,"uid":979